\super o}{C (ho\'c6c 25 }{\super o}{C). Ghi k\'d5t qu\'b6 \'aeo v\'b5o bi\'aan b\'b6n \'eb ph\'f4 l\'f4c 1.
\par 
\par 5.3.4.3 Th\'f9c hi\'d6n c\'b8c thao t\'b8c nh\'ad m\'f4c 5.3.3.2 \'ae\'e8i v\'edi dung d\'dech \'ae\'d6m chu\'c8n th\'f8 hai mang t\'ddnh ax\'ddt. Ghi k\'d5t qu\'b6 \'aeo v\'b5o bi\'aan b\'b6n \'eb ph\'f4 l\'f4c 1.
\par 
\par 5.3.4.4 Th\'f9c hi\'d6n c\'b8c thao t\'b8c nh\'ad m\'f4c 5.3.3.2 \'ae\'e8i v\'edi dung d\'dech \'ae\'d6m chu\'c8n th\'f8 ba mang t\'ddnh ki\'d2m. Ghi k\'d5t qu\'b6 \'aeo v\'b5o bi\'aan b\'b6n \'eb ph\'f4 l\'f4c 1. 
\par 
\par 5.3.4.5 Th\'f9c hi\'d6n l\'b9i l\'c7n th\'f8 hai ph\'d0p \'aeo theo quy \'ae\'denh \'eb m\'f4c 5.3.3.2, 5.3.3.3, 5.3.3.4. Ghi k\'d5t qu\'b6 \'aeo v\'b5o bi\'aan b\'b6n \'eb ph\'f4 l\'f4c 1.
